          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1692959667003-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion and carrot are softening, dissolve your<strong> beef stock mix </strong>and<strong> soy sauce </strong>in 400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[520ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [700ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1692959670975-x200.jpg",
