            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add your <strong>lean beef mince</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Once the mince has broken up, add your<strong> arborio rice </strong>and cook for 1 min further or until toasted and fully coated in the oil</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1692959679939-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
