            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and <strong>beef stock </strong>and cook for 25-30 min, stirring frequently, until all of the stock has been absorbed, the rice is cooked and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>lean beef risotto bolognese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1692959683849-x200.jpg",
