        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> lean beef risotto bolognese</strong> with the <strong>cheesy</strong> <strong>garlic & parsley croutons</strong> on top and the <strong>rocket</strong> <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> remaining chopped parsley</strong> and<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
